comment.narrative:
The number of children identified in this period was 65 (41 girls and 24 boys) children. The increase in numbers of victims safeguarded was noted following increased  deliberate efforts by LEAs in the counties. In the process of identifying cybers, video dens and villas, children around these areas and who were consumers of the content, were identified as victims and referred to service providers for relevant support.

Salaries for Project officers have all been paid as well.

The over expenditure was due to the education  and scholastic materials support offered to children. This was carried forward from previous quarters and paid in quarter 4.;
